									 <h3 :class="$style.c10" id="h.f9wv9y8bpoe"><span :class="$style.c6">Hosting and backend infrastructure</span></h3>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">This type of service has the purpose of hosting Data and files that enable SuperGreenLab to run and be distributed as well as to provide a ready-made infrastructure to run specific features or parts of SuperGreenLab.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">Some services among those listed below, if any, may work through geographically distributed servers, making it difficult to determine the actual location where the Personal Data are stored.</span></p>
									 <h3 :class="$style.c10" id="h.dgz0ee7xohc5"><span :class="$style.c6">Platform services and hosting</span></h3>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">These services have the purpose of hosting and running key components of SuperGreenLab, therefore allowing the provision of SuperGreenLab from within a unified platform. Such platforms provide a wide range of tools to the Owner &ndash; e.g. analytics, user registration, commenting, database management, e-commerce, payment processing &ndash; that imply the collection and handling of Personal Data.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">Some of these services work through geographically distributed servers, making it difficult to determine the actual location where the Personal Data are stored.</span></p>
									 <h4 :class="$style.c5" id="h.i4rjls9bvomc"><span :class="$style.c1">Google Play Store (Google LLC)</span></h4>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span>SuperGreenLab</span><span :class="$style.c2">&nbsp;is distributed on the Google Play Store, a platform for the distribution of mobile apps, provided by Google LLC.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">By virtue of being distributed via this app store, Google collects usage and diagnostics data and share aggregate information with the Owner. Much of this information is processed on an opt-in basis.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span>Users may opt-out of this analytics feature directly through their device settings. More information on how to manage analysis settings can be found on</span><span><a :class="$style.c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/6078260&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1594719390927000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0BsbjoXz_pNkcZnq28wtUA">&nbsp;</a></span><span :class="$style.c4"><a :class="$style.c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/6078260&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1594719390928000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0g3KdQ2It1NUyrwOrUBz43">this page</a></span><span :class="$style.c2">.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">Personal Data collected: Usage Data.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span>Place of processing: United States &ndash;</span><span><a :class="$style.c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://policies.google.com/privacy&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1594719390929000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3vKee6lvmwLNoqgw5rO0Ds">&nbsp;</a></span><span :class="$style.c4"><a :class="$style.c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://policies.google.com/privacy&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1594719390929000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3vKee6lvmwLNoqgw5rO0Ds">Privacy Policy</a></span><span :class="$style.c2">. Privacy Shield participant.</span></p>
									 <h4 :class="$style.c5" id="h.at7vv478b388"><span :class="$style.c1">Apple App Store (Apple Inc.)</span></h4>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span>SuperGreenLab</span><span :class="$style.c2">&nbsp;is distributed on Apple&#39;s App Store, a platform for the distribution of mobile apps, provided by Apple Inc.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">By virtue of being distributed via this app store, Apple collects basic analytics and provides reporting features that enables the Owner to view usage analytics data and measure the performance of SuperGreenLab. Much of this information is processed on an opt-in basis.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span>Users may opt-out of this analytics feature directly through their device settings. More information on how to manage analysis settings can be found on</span><span><a :class="$style.c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT202100&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1594719390930000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1t_xPsUtNArlGNNYc2GSvM">&nbsp;</a></span><span :class="$style.c4"><a :class="$style.c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT202100&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1594719390930000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1t_xPsUtNArlGNNYc2GSvM">this page</a></span><span :class="$style.c2">.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">Personal Data collected: Usage Data.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span>Place of processing: United States &ndash;</span><span><a :class="$style.c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1594719390931000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2aXJCwCei76gmE26NBF2J7">&nbsp;</a></span><span :class="$style.c4"><a :class="$style.c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1594719390931000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2aXJCwCei76gmE26NBF2J7">Privacy Policy</a></span><span :class="$style.c2">. Privacy Shield participant.</span></p>
									 <h3 :class="$style.c10" id="h.5o2lwwhx0iiy"><span :class="$style.c6">Registration and authentication</span></h3>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">By registering or authenticating, Users allow SuperGreenLab to identify them and give them access to dedicated services.</span></p>
									 <p :class="$style.c0"><span :class="$style.c2">Depending on what is described below, third parties may provide registration and authentication services. In this case, SuperGreenLab will be able to access some Data, stored by these third-party services, for registration or identification purposes.</span></p>
